text: kraoyomk a l laoh ban banhchouh pheap nungonr robsa trong towleu anakneasar robsa trong ning puok del mean chomnue( aoy mean smartei brayoutth laengvinh) . haey trong ban banhchouh kangtp( mea la- ai kat mk chuoy puok anak) del puok anak min bankheunh ke haey trong kaban dak tearounakamm towleu puok del ban brachheang . noh haey ku chea kar tabasnang champoh puok del brachheang
